criteria.driver_alignment:
Implemented — built explicit 5-year forecast and coded the assumptions into the model;  
Validate — ran a terminal-value contribution test (PV of terminal ≈ 79.8% of EV) to check forecast vs terminal balance;  
Evolve — ran downside/base/upside scenarios and a WACC vs terminal-growth sensitivity matrix to stress-test long-term growth assumptions;  
Reflect — used these results to set bid recommendations.
